# Operator-only HRR runtime flag persistence (P5.1).
# These belong in ``~/.jarvis/`` per host, never in the repo, so that the
# owner brain can opt-in to HRR/P5 while fresh clones stay safe-by-default.
runtime_flags.json
.jarvis/

